  ('medical-tech-moex-02815', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某某病病人人這這幾幾年年健健檢檢都都被被發發現現泛泛血血球球減減少少，而且好像越來愈厲害，尤其是貧血。血血液液中中沒沒有有發發現現對對抗抗紅紅血血球球 的特殊抗體，但但周周邊邊血血液液用用流流式式細細胞胞儀儀檢檢查查結結果果如如圖圖示示。則則此此病病人人最最可可能能罹罹患患下下列列何何種種疾疾病病？', '["G6PD缺乏症，俗稱的蠶豆症", "再生不良性貧血（aappllaassttiicc  aanneemmiiaa,,  AAAA）", "陣發性夜間血色素尿（ppaarrooxxyyssmmaall  nnooccttuurrnnaall  hheemmoogglloobbiinnuurriiaa,,  PPNNHH）", "陣發性冷性血色素尿（ppaarrooxxyyssmmaall  ccoolldd  hheemmoogglloobbiinnuurriiaa,,  PPCCHH）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "141dd4630ba7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fa2dcee952cb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02816', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '當病人鉛中毒時，下下列列何何者者會會明明顯顯出出現現於於病病人人周周邊邊血血液液抹抹片片的的紅紅血血球球內內？', '["Howell-Jolly bodies", "Siderotic granules", "Basophilic stippling", "Heinz bodies"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "141dd4630ba7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fa2dcee952cb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
